/-- Canonical rational-gamma off-diagonal-control handoff with both
    source-nonbreakdown inputs derived from the signed Householder definition.

    This is the algorithm-facing sibling of
    `StoredQROffDiagonalControlInvariant.of_diagDominant_leadingBlock_det_ne_zero_finiteMaxSourceDenURationalGammaCanonicalBounds`:
    callers provide the concrete signed-alpha formula used by the stored QR
    loop, and the theorem derives the two scalar signed-alpha facts internally.
